//        &kp S   &lt NUM H   &hm LCMD N    &hm LSHFT T   &kp COMMA       &kp DOT     &hm RSHFT E     &hm RCMD A       &kp I     &kp O
//        &kp F   &kp M       &kp V         &kp C         &none           &none       &kp P           &kp X            &kp K     &kp Y
